<h5>Add-Ons</h5>
<p>Add-ons are used to extend the functionality of Campaign Press past its core purpose.  Below are a list of available &amp; installed add-ons.</p>
<h5>Installing Add-Ons</h5>
<p>Once you've purchased and downloaded an Add-On from the <a href="http://floatingmonk.co.nz/campaignpress/">Campaign Press website</a>, extract the add-on folder from the zip file and place it in the <code>/addons/</code> folder within the plugin folder structure.  That will install the Add-On and active its functionality automatically.</p>